&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The position of Store Lead is responsible for supervising, managing and motivating team members daily. This position prioritizes a focus on long term growth and development within our exceptional organization and the cannabis community. The Store Lead is a first level Supervisor, who are passionate about excellent customer service, consistent communication skills, teamwork and driving maximum results; takes initiative in being action oriented in order to keep frontline operations running smoothly and collaborate for solutions to issues that arise.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
